Package: xMSannotator
Type: Package
Title: Network-Based Annotation of Untargeted Metabolomics Data
Version: 1.4.6
Date: 2026-03-22
Authors@R: 
    person("Karan", "Uppal",
           email = "kuppal3gt@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides algorithms for metabolite annotation using
    correlation networks, isotope patterns, and database matching.
    The package supports annotation using HMDB, KEGG, LipidMaps,
    T3DB, and user-defined databases, and includes utilities for
    querying KEGG through the REST API.
